title: She Was Impressed Until He Did This...
description:
She met the guy last week and he checked all the boxes that she would want on a list for a romantic partner. But after two dates, things start to get a little weird. The guy tells her that he is tired of committed relationships and that he could see himself in a serious relationship with her.
